itemLabel: George William Michael Chubb, 4th Baron Hayter

wikipedia_page.main: George William Michael Chubb, 4th Baron Hayter (born 9 October 1943) is a British businessman. He is the son of George Charles Hayter Chubb, 3rd Baron Hayter (1911–2003), and the great-great-great grandson of Charles Chubb (1772–1845), who had founded Chubb and Sons Lock and Safe Co.
